commit.message:
Skip GitLab CI environment variables that contain secrets

`CI_JOB_TOKEN`, `CI_REPOSITORY_URL` and `CI_REGISTRY_PASSWORD` are masked (the value is replaced by `[MASKED]`) by GitLab when included in the output, so it's not very useful to include them.

Skip GitLab CI environment variables that contain secrets

`CI_JOB_TOKEN`, `CI_REPOSITORY_URL` and `CI_REGISTRY_PASSWORD` are masked (the value is replaced by `[MASKED]`) by GitLab when included in the output, so it's not very useful to include them.
